---
title: reserve_price_check (EIP-7918)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init
    q_init --> q_compute_reserve : reserve_price = BLOB_BASE_COST * parent.base_fee_per_gas
    q_compute_reserve --> q_compute_blob_cost : blob_cost = GAS_PER_BLOB * get_base_fee_per_blob_gas(parent)
    q_compute_blob_cost --> q_below_reserve : reserve_price > blob_cost
    q_compute_blob_cost --> q_above_reserve : reserve_price <= blob_cost
    q_below_reserve --> q_final : return EXEC_FEE_LED
    q_above_reserve --> q_final : return BLOB_FEE_LED
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_compute_blob_cost
        INV-008: BLOB_BASE_COST = 2^13 = 8192
        INV-009: Reserve ratio BLOB_BASE_COST / GAS_PER_BLOB = 1/16
        INV-010: Reserve price scales linearly with execution base fee
    end note
